---
title: Moroccan Chickpea Veggie, Chicken & Currant Stew with Mash & Almonds
description: Bring the warm Moroccan flavours to your table in the form of a stew packed on top of a blanket of mashed potato. The comforting addition of chickpeas, chicken and spices is everything this stew needs to end a long day.

*We’ve replaced the lentils in this recipe with chickpeas due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
